title: Fun with Easy Origami: 32 Projects
description:
Fun with Easy Origami: 32 Projects and 24 Sheets of Origami Paper (Dover Origami Papercraft) by Dover

English | Mar. 22, 1993 | ISBN: 0486274802 | 49 Pages | PDF | 27 MB


Inside this handy folder is everything a beginner needs to practice the ancient Japanese art of paper folding, including a clearly illustrated instructional booklet and a packet of authentic origami paper.

Also included are directions for more challenging but still easy-to-make subjects such as a pigeon, pelican, and piano
